    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>書いたのではっとく</p>

<p><div><script src='https://gist.github.com/4122658.js'></script>
<noscript><pre><code>#!/bin/sh

TODAY=`date +%Y%m%d`
DIR=&quot;/path/to/dir&quot;
DAYS=60

find ${DIR} -type f -name '*.log' -daystart -mtime +${DAYS} | while read f; do
    nice tar czfv ${f}.tgz --directory `dirname ${f}` `basename ${f}`
    rm ${f}
done</code></pre></noscript></div>
